original: Your natural hair color is (or was) blonde.
translation: 你的自然发色是金色的。

original: Your natural eye color is a bright blue.
translation: 你天生的眼睛颜色是明亮的蓝色。

original: An arrow decorated with a pretty red ribbon, making them easy to find and recover after battle.
translation: 用漂亮的红丝带装饰的箭，使它们在战斗后很容易找到和恢复。

original: This folding 2L bottle is made out of a proprietary A&M plastic of reduced weight. It did not sell well initially, but became a valuable collectors item once produciton ended.
translation: 这款折叠2L瓶子由a&M专有塑料制成，重量减轻。它最初并不畅销，但一旦生产结束，它就成了收藏家的珍品。

original: Use this to send a request for an item from the A&M dimensional transfer system.
translation: 使用此选项从a&M维度传输系统发送项目请求。

original: Although I worked in a large mansion, the day the cataclysm, my master's family fled to a secret location I did not know of. You were alone with a dirty house, and a cluttered city. It's time to go to work.
translation: 虽然我在一个大宅子里工作，但灾难发生的那天，我主人的家人逃到了一个我不知道的秘密地点。你一个人住着一所肮脏的房子，一个杂乱无章的城市。该上班了。

original: For exclusive use in A&M Products。
After months in seculusion and prayer at our underground church, we visited the surface to find the world was completely changed. There is no need for despair, for God is with us.
translation: 我们在地下教堂做了几个月的祈祷和祈祷后，我们来到了地表，发现世界完全改变了。没有必要绝望，因为上帝与我们同在。

original: Your natural hair color is (or was) red.
translation: 你的自然发色是红色的。

original: Your natural eye color is a dark blue.
translation: 你天生的眼睛颜色是深蓝色。

original: An arrow decorated with the brightly coloured flight feathers of birds. These are appear of exceptional craftsmanship, being lighter yet stronger than standard arrows, and consequently more likely to be recovered after combat since they are less likely to break.
translation: 装饰有鸟的鲜艳羽毛的箭。这些箭看起来有着非凡的工艺，比标准箭更轻更坚固，因此在战斗后更有可能被回收，因为它们不太可能折断。

original: This 10L jerrycan is made out of a proprietary A&M plastic of reduced weight. It did not sell well initially, but became a valuable collectors item once produciton ended.
translation: 这款10L的jerrycan由a&M专有塑料制成，重量减轻。它最初并不畅销，但一旦生产结束，它就成了收藏家的珍品。

original: Use this to send away an item to the A&M dimensional transfer system in exchange for points.
translation: 使用此选项将项目发送到A&M维度传输系统以交换点数。

original: I used to think it would be nice if school closed forever. Now that the cataclysm has happened, it seems my wish has come true.
translation: 我曾经认为如果学校永远关闭会很好。既然灾难发生了，我的愿望似乎实现了。

original: Your natural hair color is (or was) brown.
translation: 你的自然发色是棕色的。

original: Your natural eye color is a bright brown.
translation: 你天生的眼睛颜色是明亮的棕色。

original: An arrow manufactured by the 'Alice & Maria' maid equipment designers. These aren't arrows so much as smart projectiles, having very dense alloy cores for greater force and a tip sheathed in an electromagnetic field to better penetrate armor.
translation: “爱丽丝和玛丽亚”女仆设备设计师制造的箭头。这些箭与其说是智能射弹，不如说是箭，它有非常致密的合金核以获得更大的威力，其尖端被电磁场包裹以更好地穿透装甲。

original: This 20L jerrycan is made out of a proprietary A&M plastic of reduced weight. It did not sell well initially, but became a valuable collectors item once produciton ended.
translation: 这款20L的jerrycan由a&M专有塑料制成，重量减轻。它最初并不畅销，但一旦生产结束，它就成了收藏家的珍品。

original: This device allows you to see how much currency you've accumulated for use with the A&M dimensional transfer system.
translation: 这个设备可以让你看到有多少货币你已经积累使用A&M维度转移系统。

original: Your natural hair color is (or was) black.
translation: 你的头发本来是黑色的。

original: Your natural eye color is a dark brown.
translation: 你天生的眼睛颜色是深棕色。

original: This is a packaging system for use with the A&M dimensional transfer system. It can be used to compress raw material into a single package which can be sent to the AMTS in exchange for points.
translation: 这是用于a&M尺寸转移系统的包装系统。它可以用来压缩成一个单一的包装，可以发送到AMTS在交换点的原材料。

original: Your natural hair color is (or was) white.
translation: 你的自然发色是白色的。

original: Your natural eye color is a bright gray.
translation: 你天生的眼睛颜色是明亮的灰色。

original: An A&M compressed matter package ready for dimensional transfer. It can be exchanged for points.
translation: A&M压缩物质包，准备进行空间转移。可以兑换积分。

original: Your natural hair color is (or was) grey.
translation: 你天生的头发颜色是灰色的。

original: Your natural eye color is a dark gray.
translation: 你天生的眼睛颜色是深灰色。

original: Your natural hair color is (or was) pink.
translation: 你的自然发色是粉红色。

original: Your natural eye color is a bright red.
translation: 你天生的眼睛颜色是鲜红的。

original: Your natural hair color is (or was) orange.
Your natural eye color is a dark red.
translation: 你天生的眼睛颜色是暗红色。

original: Your natural hair color is (or was) blue.
translation: 你的自然发色是蓝色的。

original: Your natural eye color is a bright green.
translation: 你天生的眼睛颜色是明亮的绿色。

original: Your natural hair color is (or was) green.
translation: 你的自然发色是绿色的。

original: Your natural eye color is a dark green.
translation: 你天生的眼睛颜色是深绿色。

original: Your natural hair color is (or was) aqua.
translation: 你的自然发色是（或曾经是）水绿色。

original: Your natural eye color is a bright yellow.
translation: 你天生的眼睛颜色是明亮的黄色。

original: Your natural hair color is (or was) purple.
Your natural eye color is a dark yellow.
translation: 你天生的眼睛颜色是深黄色。

original: A UPS by A&M that stores more charge with less weight than standard UPS modules.
translation: A&M公司生产的一种UPS，比标准的UPS模块存储更多的电量，重量更小。

original: Your natural eye color is a bright purple.
translation: 你天生的眼睛颜色是明亮的紫色。

original: A&M manufactured portable cooking set. There are supposedly very few of these made due to the extrordinary costs, a direct consequence of using A&M's proprietary advanced alloy in its construction.
translation: A&M制造的便携式炊具。据推测，由于使用a&M专有的先进合金建造的直接后果，超常规成本造成的此类产品很少。

original: Your natural eye color is a dark purple.
translation: 你天生的眼睛颜色是深紫色。

original: An advanced prototype rifle. Has both semi-automatic and two-round burst firing modes.
translation: 一种先进的步枪原型。有两个半自动和两个回合突发发射模式。

original: Your natural skin color is (or was) rather pale.
translation: 你天生的肤色相当苍白。

original: Exlusively for use with the AMTS Eve Scout Rifle. It holds 20 rounds.
translation: 专用于AMTS Eve侦察步枪。它有20发子弹。

original: A manual for Alice & Maria employees. It explains how to pack items for use with the AMTS packaging system.
translation: Alice&Maria员工手册。它解释了如何包装物品与AMTS包装系统一起使用。

original: <color_pink>[AMTS]</color> A&M Employee's Manual Tier 2 (About Efficient Packaging)
translation: <color_pink>[AMTS]</color>A&M员工手册第2层（关于高效包装）

original: A manual for Alice & Maria employees. It explains how to effiently pack items for use with the AMTS packaging system.
translation: Alice&Maria员工手册。它解释了如何有效地包装物品与AMTS包装系统一起使用。

original: <color_pink>[AMTS]</color> A&M Employee's Manual Tier 3 (About Gear Packaging)
translation: <color_pink>[AMTS]</color>A&M员工手册第3层（关于齿轮包装）

original: A manual for Alice & Maria employees. It explains how to pack gear for use with the AMTS packaging system.
translation: Alice&Maria员工手册。它解释了如何包装与AMTS包装系统使用的齿轮。

original: <color_pink>[AMTS]</color> A&M Employee's Manual Tier Kawaii (About Kawaii Packaging)
A manual for Alice & Maria employees. It explains how to pack kawaii items for use with the AMTS packaging system.
translation: Alice&Maria员工手册。它解释了如何包装kawaii项目与AMTS包装系统一起使用。

original: Made out of the hopes and dreams of men.
translation: 是由男人的希望和梦想造成的。

original: Includes high-tech transformable melee weapons, a remotely-access store, and of course, cute outfits for maids.
translation: 包括高科技的可转换近战武器，远程访问商店，当然，可爱的女仆服装。
可爱的女仆。制服（夏季版）

original: Centuries of maid sewing techniques have culminated in this pinnacle of maid outfit technology: an year-round outfit that can be transformed to fit any weather or season.
translation: 几百年的女仆缝纫技术达到了女仆服装技术的顶峰：一套全年都可以改变的服装，可以适应任何天气或季节。
可爱的女仆。制服（冬季版）

original: The standard maid uniform may not be enough to survive in this dangerous new world. This improved version, while still appearing cute and frilly on the outside, actually conceals an advanced armor liner and climate control systems to better endure even the harshest environments.
translation: 标准的女仆制服可能不足以在这个危险的新世界生存。这一改进版，虽然外表看起来仍然可爱和褶边，实际上隐藏了先进的装甲衬里和气候控制系统，以更好地忍受甚至最恶劣的环境。
可爱的维多利亚女仆服装

original: A uniform with longer sleeves and skirt, better suited for winter.
translation: 长袖长裙的制服，更适合冬天穿。

original: A nun's habit for serving God that gives off a sacred aura.
translation: 修女服侍上帝的习惯，散发出神圣的光环。
可爱的透明雨衣（带风帽）

original: A transparent raincoat made from very thin vinyl, very popular with maids who want to be fashionable in rainy weather. The material is thin enough that the entire coat can fold away into a pocket when not in use.
translation: 一种透明的雨衣，由非常薄的乙烯基制成，非常受想要在雨天时髦的女仆们的欢迎。这种材料很薄，不用时整个外套可以折叠起来放进口袋里。

original: A transparent raincoat made from very thin vinyl, very popular with maids who want to be fashionable in rainy wather. The material is thin enough that the entire coat can fold away into a pocket when not in use.
translation: 一种透明的雨衣，由非常薄的乙烯基制成，非常受想要在雨天时髦的女仆们的欢迎。这种材料很薄，不用时整个外套可以折叠起来放进口袋里。

original: A school uniform worn by female students.
Pure white panties, very breathable and comfortable even in summer.
translation: 纯白色内裤，即使在夏天也非常透气舒适。

original: Pure white bra, very breathable and comfortable even in summer.
translation: 纯白色胸罩，即使在夏天也非常透气舒适。
可爱的黑色比基尼底裤
一个简单的黑色比基尼底部。
可爱的黑色比基尼上衣
一件简单的黑色比基尼上衣。

original: A flared miniskirt that is longer in the back.
translation: 后面较长的喇叭口迷你裙。

original: A modified utility vest with many pockets.
translation: 有许多口袋的改良实用背心。

original: One of the most important parts of the maid uniform. It is forbidden for maids to take it off, regardless of weather. Trained maids can channel their spirit into it to keep their heads warm during winter. (Toggle to change warmth)
translation: 女仆制服最重要的部分之一。无论天气如何，女佣都不准脱。训练有素的女佣们可以将他们的精神导入其中，使他们的头在冬天保持温暖。（切换以更改温度）
可爱的保暖女仆头饰（关）

original: One of the most important parts of the maid unifrom is the headdress. This one contains an electrical thermal system powedered using batteries. It lets you feel like a maid despite how it looks.
translation: 女仆制服最重要的部分之一是头饰。这个系统包含一个用电池供电的电热系统。它让你感觉像个女仆，不管它看起来怎么样。
可爱的保暖女仆头饰（上）

original: A maid must maintain her pride and attends to her duties, no matter how harsh the situation or environment. The headdress is not just a piece of the uniform, it's a symbol of a maid's pride.
translation: 无论环境多么恶劣，女仆都必须保持自尊心，尽职尽责。头饰不仅仅是制服的一部分，它是女仆骄傲的象征。

original: These advanced glasses are not only capable of functioning as night vision or infared scanners, but protects against bright flashes, can withstand chemical corrosion, and can even completely block light for sleeping in bright places.
translation: 这些先进的眼镜不仅能起到夜视或红外扫描仪的作用，而且能防止闪光，能抵抗化学腐蚀，甚至能完全阻挡光线，让人睡在明亮的地方。
可爱的高科技眼镜（盲人）

original: A maid wearing these will never miss the smallest speck of dust, nor signs of their master's health. (Toggle to adjust position)
translation: 一个女仆穿上这些衣服，决不会错过一点灰尘，也不会错过主人健康的迹象。（切换以调整位置）
可爱的黑色大半框眼镜

original: A maid wearing these will never miss the smallest speck of dust, nor signs of their master's health.
translation: 一个女仆穿上这些衣服，决不会错过一点灰尘，也不会错过主人健康的迹象。

original: It's a warm hat made of cotton, coloured white to better match a maid uniform.
translation: 这是一顶温暖的棉帽，颜色为白色，以更好地搭配女仆制服。

original: 'I refuse to cover up my cute face!' It's not as good against the cold as a normal balaclava, but it's a sacrifice necessary for the sake of fashion.
translation: “我拒绝遮住我可爱的脸！”它的抗寒能力不如普通的巴拉克拉瓦，但这是为了时尚而必须做出的牺牲。

original: A beautiful but simple wedding veil.
A beautiful wedding veil with additional adornments.
translation: 带有附加装饰的漂亮的结婚面纱。

original: A veil worn by those devoted to serving God.
translation: 献身于服侍上帝的人所戴的面纱。
可爱的长波浪粉色假发

original: A wig with long, wavy pink hair.
translation: 长着粉红色波浪长发的假发。

original: A huge rectangular hardcase. Normally used for carrying large musical instruments, sniper rifles, or sensitive electrical equipment.
translation: 一个巨大的长方形精装书。通常用于携带大型乐器、狙击步枪或敏感的电气设备。

original: A smaller version of the standard hardcase.
A slimmer version of the hardcase.
A small storage purse that can be consealed beneath a skirt, held up using a garter band.
translation: 一个小的储物钱包，可以藏在裙子下面，用吊袜带绑住。

original: A pair of frilly kneesocks. Its thick material keeps the wearer's legs warm.
translation: 一双褶边短袜。它的厚材料使穿着者的腿保持温暖。

original: A pair of frilly kneesocks. Its thin enough to be slightly transparent when worn.
translation: 一双褶边短袜。它足够薄，佩戴时略微透明。

original: A pair of white socks normally worn by students.
translation: 学生通常穿的一双白袜子。

original: A black garter belt, designed to be worn with stockings.
translation: 一条黑色吊袜带，设计用来搭配长袜。

original: Leather shoes designed to be worn with a maid uniform.
translation: 设计成与女仆制服一起穿的皮鞋。

original: A pair of brown loafers normally worn by students.
translation: 学生通常穿的一双棕色休闲鞋。

original: Leather boots that can be worn with a wide range of outfits.
translation: 可以搭配各种服装的皮靴。

original: Pure white boots that only chosen maids are allowed to wear. They give the wearer a feeling of majesty.
translation: 只允许挑选的女仆穿的纯白靴子。它们给佩戴者一种威严的感觉。

original: Pure white heels that only chosen maids are allowed to wear. They give the wearer a feeling of majesty.
translation: 只有被选中的女仆才能穿的纯白色高跟鞋。它们给佩戴者一种威严的感觉。

original: A scarf with a cute pattern.
A hand-made bow made that has been very carefully decorated and painted. It's more a costume accessory than a deadly weapon.
translation: 一种手工制作的蝴蝶结，经过非常仔细的装饰和油漆。与其说是致命武器，不如说是化装配件。

original: A handcrafted bow assembled with an experienced hand, from scavenged materials.
translation: 一种手工制作的弓，由一只有经验的手用捡来的材料组装而成。

original: It is an improved version of the Cutie Custom Bow Mk1. The performance improved greatly by reinforcing the frame with steel, but consequently is larger and heavier than its predecessor
translation: 这是一个可爱的自定义弓Mk1的改进版本。通过用钢加固框架，性能大大提高，但因此比以前的框架更大、更重

original: It is an improved version of the Cutie Custom Bow Mk2. The frame has been made even larger and reinforced with higher quality materials than its predecessor. Consequently, it is an excellent bow that looks like it was made by a master craftsman.
translation: 这是一个可爱的自定义弓Mk2的改进版本。该框架已作出更大，并加强了更高质量的材料比其前身。因此，这是一个优秀的弓，看起来像是由一个大师工匠。

original: This is a very heavy bow with a sharp steel spike protruding from the front. It's much harder to shoot accurately, but can endure close combat much better than regular bows.
translation: 这是一个非常沉重的弓，有一个尖锐的钢钉从前面突出。精确射击要困难得多，但比普通弓箭更能忍受近战。

original: This device is a complex transforming weapon capable of becoming either a bladed melee weapon, or a powerful bow. This is the first release in the [Cute Combat] series of of stylish protective equipment by the world's leading maid fashion brand Alice & Maria. The weapon itself proved to be quite desirable, as it could transform for engaging foes at both long range and in close combat. However, it ended up earning the nickname 'Nighmarish Shelia' due to its overly complex design making it too expensive for the mass market, and bankrupting its designer.
translation: 这个装置是一个复杂的转换武器，可以成为一个刀片式近战武器，或一个强大的弓。这是世界著名女仆时尚品牌Alice&Maria推出的[可爱战斗]系列时尚防护装备的首次发布。事实证明，这种武器本身是非常理想的，因为它可以在远程和近距离战斗中转变为与敌人交战的武器。然而，由于其过于复杂的设计使其在大众市场上过于昂贵，最终赢得了“Nighmarish Shelia”的绰号，并使其设计师破产。

original: An elegant bow decorated with angelic feathers at each end, and possessing a strong metal handguard. This is the second product in the series of fashionable self-defense tools [Cute Combat] series revealed by the world's leading maid fashion brand Alice & Maria. The material used for the metal plate was announced at the same time as the same product, it was expected to be a next generation alloy that possesses flexibility and durability despite being very light, but it was too expensive to mass produce. Consequently this weapon only sold a limited number.
translation: 一种优雅的蝴蝶结，两端饰有天使般的羽毛，有一个坚固的金属护手。这是全球著名女仆时尚品牌Alice&Maria推出的时尚自卫工具[可爱格斗]系列中的第二款产品。金属板所用的材料与同一产品同时公布，预计它将是下一代合金，尽管重量很轻，但仍具有灵活性和耐用性，但成本太高，无法批量生产。因此这种武器的销量有限。

original: The daikyu is the traditional Japanese equivalent of the longbow. It's a complex weapon to master, but has enough power to penetrate even the heaviest armor.
translation: 大船是日本传统的长弓。这是一个复杂的武器掌握，但有足够的力量穿透甚至最重的盔甲。

original: A heavy translucent glass bow, made possible due to the integration of carbom nanotubes into its structure.
translation: 一个沉重的半透明玻璃弓，由于碳纳米管的结构整合成为可能。
可爱的丽塔和罗莎（防御模式）

original: A matching set of sword and shield by the world's leading maid fashion brand Alice & Maria, made out of a proprietary advanced alloy. The blade 'Rita' is long enough to allow strikes with extended reach, yet still remaining light enough to wield one-handed. The shield 'Rosa' is similarly very strong yet light, granding defence on par with steel but being light enough to not encumber movement.
translation: 由世界领先的女仆时尚品牌Alice&Maria设计的一套剑和盾，由专有的高级合金制成。“丽塔”刀足够长，可以让攻击范围扩大，但仍然保持轻到足以挥舞一只手。“罗莎”盾同样非常坚固，但重量很轻，防御力与钢铁相当，但重量足够轻，不会妨碍移动。
可爱的丽塔和罗莎（攻击模式）

original: It is a pair of short swords that are beautifully transparency and glossy
translation: 这是一把透明而有光泽的短剑

original: A two-ended polearm composed of beautifully crystalline swords attached together at the hilt.
translation: 一种两头的剑，由漂亮的水晶剑组成，剑柄处连在一起。

original: A beautiful two-ended polearm with beautiful crystalline blades... though it seems pretty fragile.
translation: 一个美丽的两端有美丽的水晶刀片的极地。。。虽然它看起来很脆弱。

original: A rusty spear made from a piece of steel. Despite being cheap, it still allows you to keep your distance from the undead.
translation: 铁制的生锈的矛。尽管价格便宜，它仍然能让你与亡灵保持距离。

original: An improved version of the Custom Spear (Ver.1). A practical, easy to use weapon, the rust has been removed with a piece of glass and careful polishing. In addition, the grip has been reinforced for increased durability.
translation: 改进版的定制长矛（1版）。一个实用的，易于使用的武器，锈迹已经消除了一块玻璃和仔细抛光。此外，抓地力已得到加强，以提高耐用性。

original: An improved version of the Custom Spear (Ver.2). The tip has been further sharpened and reinforced, increasing its range and killing ability. An improved hand guard allows for greater effectiveness at close-range. A blue ribbon has been attached to it.
translation: 改进版的定制长矛（版本2）。尖端被进一步锐化和强化，增加了射程和杀伤力。一个改进的护手允许在近距离更有效。一条蓝丝带系在上面。

original: A big scythe, rumored to have been used by shinigami (death spirits)
translation: 一把大镰刀，据传是shinigami（死神）用过的

original: Rather than a knife and fork set, this a pair of knives. It may not be proper etiquette at the table, but it's proper etiquette in combat.
translation: 这不是刀叉套装，而是一把刀。这也许不是餐桌上的礼节，但却是战斗中的礼节。

original: A quality handmade short sword. Probably the best that could be done without proper smithing tools.
translation: 一把高质量的手工短剑。如果没有合适的锻造工具，可能是最好的方法。

original: A lance composed of multiple crowbars made of Alice and Maria's proprietary advanced alloy. Crude, but functional.
translation: 由爱丽丝和玛丽亚专有的高级合金制成的多个撬棍组成的长矛。简陋但实用。
